{"tid":808432,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"上手做得差，搞到我俾人針對","createTime":"2018-09-06T10:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T03:47:16.000Z","uid":61586,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"038e44b09c09d95d02ff888bf93245b5f2e344d2","tid":808432,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"上手返工渣流灘，做野恰眼訓，無做話做左，乜鳩都唔識，遲到早退，最後俾變態女上司迫走<br />\n<br />\n我唔知頭唔知路過左去，以為都係普通料<br />\n做左一年，日日俾人針，同佢講有問題，佢第一個反應係我唔識（因為上手係咁搵藉口）<br />\n做幾多都唔滿意，行政以外我要睇哂，但唔保證行政野我唔洗做。<br />\n做左成年都當我外人，成日搵鳩我笨，同總部有牙齒印又搵我頂，拎我祭旗。<br />\n啲舊人有一兩個唔得佢歡心，走黎同我講老實話我先知有歷史背景。<br />\n<br />\n而家我按章工作唔同佢搏殺，佢憎撚到我死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三萬工周街都係，做撚埋個年尾唔柒做，就算搵少啲都唔想幫人執手尾。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05b2251b2446d3ba6d88bde71a3018e58ef276f","tid":808432,"uid":74927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"咁又岩呀 如果你搵得番呢個價 做乜鳩留係到<br />\n番工都唔開心點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a736f443b8e7117fec32514f3c634d22f590de7a","tid":808432,"uid":75692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"返工除左錢之外<br />\n工作關係 同事上司都重要<br />\n因為返工時間仲耐過對屋企人"},{"pid":"3df395d90b05a679eb781fe6f3c735d9761cdd31","tid":808432,"uid":203889,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得問題唔係上手而係個on9上司"},{"pid":"6a4a9f47ef07970e278c7f7c117ecc426db4b176","tid":808432,"uid":50740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:12:17.000Z","msg":"周街30000蚊仲唔走人?"},{"pid":"d974e6106590a8fded51c84aea297a2c097c0bb7","tid":808432,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"其實其他同事都好好<br />\n有唔甘心，地點近都係其中原因<br />\n去到邊都有辦公室問題，正常都要面對<br />\n<br />\n今次努力左一年，係時候放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f849351c68e8863a9c181d73dea74122c1544c50","tid":808432,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"呢d工返一個月唔對路都即走啦,仲一年"},{"pid":"6255bd19511fee28ad1446f5085e7529c70047e5","tid":808432,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦提3萬做乜鳩"},{"pid":"6e1494b6b703aeb9220899ba142322d0ba199200","tid":808432,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6255bd19511fee28ad1446f5085e7529c70047e5","tid":808432,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦提3萬做乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"3萬算係大部份人都搵到既數"},{"pid":"4f441b022eed196de5a35af04c016a3fd0e15e5f","tid":808432,"uid":6329,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6e1494b6b703aeb9220899ba142322d0ba199200","tid":808432,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6255bd19511fee28ad1446f5085e7529c70047e5","tid":808432,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無啦啦提3萬做乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"3萬算係大部份人都搵到既數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"3萬FG都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a5089c4d67a19d221231060d13ba72583ef32","tid":808432,"uid":192158,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:58:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03c558b9d8e945bfd4cdd9ecdba97d3b4e399d47","tid":808432,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:34:37.000Z","msg":"三萬工周街都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cab5f30e2a718162871b4b328303dcb11d8f72","tid":808432,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:53:24.000Z","msg":"想做3萬工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af80488ea2444c9a63ffa6f9413acf04fe4e26d","tid":808432,"uid":17777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"535a5089c4d67a19d221231060d13ba72583ef32","tid":808432,"uid":192158,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4f441b022eed196de5a35af04c016a3fd0e15e5f","tid":808432,"uid":6329,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6e1494b6b703aeb9220899ba142322d0ba199200","tid":808432,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"3萬算係大部份人都搵到既數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"3萬FG都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T16:58:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"FG 是但搵份工都45K up <br />\n<br />\n30k 一開始就應該reject offer la"},{"pid":"5116df423057069e80b33f5d38a9a8efdbf38d79","tid":808432,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"同一行跳跳下有咁上下年資<br />\n有咁上下價錢好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講，三萬係香港真係唔算多⋯<br />\n<br />\n開頭我諗住係人夾人問題，我解決到佢嘅困難慢慢就會改變，無可能一兩個月就見真章，但係我前園撲火佢後欄點火，無一百都幾十單<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢度幾多假膠啦⋯<br />\n我出黎做野果陣先9000蚊，做左四五份工先到30k<br />\n閪人遇過唔少，但通常都係無前景先走<br />\n因人事問題真係第一次⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所有FG出黎都45k?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你認真就on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cdff413bad0966c2b6ea92f9abcedb07820281","tid":808432,"uid":5125